branchCategory.name: ISE2, Pressure Switch, 1 Output, LED Indicator
branchCategory.description: <p>ISE2 is a basic pressure switch with 1 digital output (NPN or PNP).  No analog output is included.  The ISE2 monitors the pressure of any non-corrosive, non-flammable gas.  Low and high pressure ranges are offered, as well as metric or NPTF male thread connections.  A rotary trimmer adjusts the switch set point.  A red LED indicator also lights to correspond with the output signal.  Electrical connections include a 3 wire grommet cable or 3 wire snap-in connector.  ISE2 is CE and RoHS compliant, with an IP40 enclosure rating.</p>
